translate spanish kendra0_48413cfa:

    # "I go to the park and spot a group of people at the skate park, riding around and doing tricks."
    "Voy al parque y veo a un grupo de gente en el skatepark, dando vueltas y haciendo trucos."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/kendra0.rpy:13
translate spanish kendra0_aef10dea:

    # "They pay no attention to me as I walk over and sit at a nearby bench. "
    "No me prestan atención mientras me acerco y me siento en un banco cercano. "

# game/Scenes/Kendra/kendra0.rpy:15
translate spanish kendra0_be217211:

    # "One of the skaters in particular catches my attention"
    "Una de las skaters en particular me llama la atención."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/kendra0.rpy:16
translate spanish kendra0_51b805e1:

    # "It's a girl with multi-colored dreadlocks that I am pretty sure are fake."
    "Es una chica con rastas multicolores que estoy bastante seguro de que son postizas."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/kendra0.rpy:17
translate spanish kendra0_16441d49:

    # "She wears a pair of baggy pants and a crop-top shirt that her breasts frequently threaten to escape from. "
    "Lleva unos pantalones holgados y una camiseta corta de la que sus pechos amenazan con salirse a menudo."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/kendra0.rpy:19
translate spanish kendra0_9180aac9:

    # "I watch as she performs stunts on the skateboard that I can barely even comprehend. "
    "La observo mientras realiza acrobacias en la tabla de skate que apenas puedo comprender."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/kendra0.rpy:20
translate spanish kendra0_6ecfc325:

    # "She seems really into it, not paying attention to anything happening outside of her skateboard."
    "Parece muy metida en ello, sin prestar atención a nada de lo que ocurre fuera de su tabla."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/kendra0.rpy:22
translate spanish kendra0_65bf7335:

    # "After some time, she notices me watching and smiles at me, but doesn't say anything and then continues skating. "
    "Al cabo de un rato, se da cuenta de que la estoy mirando y me sonríe, pero no dice nada y sigue patinando. "

# game/Scenes/Kendra/kendra0.rpy:23
translate spanish kendra0_c65360e2:

    # "I watch for a while longer before deciding to head back to my car."
    "La observo un rato más antes de decidir volver al coche."

